<br>
1.) there are some books in PoK that deal with the unkempt druids. Sure there was some lore about an old wolf type race.<br>
<br>
2.) Sentry Alechin in south karana was a human bitten and turned into a were wolf.<br>
<br>
3.) werewolves are only around human based area's, Elves had unicorns humans had werewolves.<br>
<br>
4.) there are kobolds afflicted with lycahtropy in the warrens.<br>
<br>
Vampire's are kind of different because they have a few different representations.<br>
<br>
1.) all EQ vampires are flagged as undead (as far as i know)<br>
<br>
2.) I have never heard a story or text or quest or anything that says people can be bitten and turned into a vampire.<br>
<br>
Vampires in tower of shadow actually can turn into bats and have other skills like &quot;vampiric charm&quot; they also have pools of blood in there living quarters - also there skin tone is significant.. they are all dark elven with very pale skin, well they are dead and hence pale and still keep a blue hue to there skin, also other obvious dark elven features - white hair, ears, size etc and also location.<br>
<br>
No idea what the luclin vampires are, they dont fit in really.<br>
<br>
Then you have the vampires in the mistmoor expansion - these look more high elven - add names like Trueborn........<br>
<br>
I dont think they can make up there mind on vampires - they basically changed from standard undead in mistmoor (cant remember if the wak blade had any info on the maid/buttler.. if they were bitten or not) to the undead in tower of shadow who had other more powerful abilitys like Vampiric charm and freedom to change into a bat.. then to vampires on luclin wich are almost there own race and culture because of a perpetual nighttime environment and eventually back to mistmoor with Ldon wich all seem to be high elves.... I am to confused what the designers really wanted out of vampires.<br>
<br>
The only thing i see consistent is that EQ vampires have inate magical abilitys to take health from there oponents - not blooddrinking... infact the only blooddrinking creatures from EQ i can think of are mosquito's.<br>
<br>
Brae<br>
