<br>
Tserrina's vampires in the Tower of Frozen Shadow are the same as Mistmoore's, except in a different environment.  I believe she and Mistmoore are or once were allies?<br>
<br>
The Coterie of the Eternal Night on Luclin is entirely Human originally, I think... they've grown so numerous that they've practically set themselves apart as a race, but they still bring in victims from Katta Castellum.<br>
<br>
I'm sure I got at least a few things wrong here... do correct me if you notice anything. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Kelisk Mae'Lokh</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Chancellor of Skathris Ven'Sho--Patriarch of Cabilis</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=112815"><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Inspect Kelisk?</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=zhillan>Zhillan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(10/6/03 4:52 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4994.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://users.zoominternet.net/~carpenoctem/zhillan.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Vampyres</span><hr size=1> This is the <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=1582" target="top">Quest</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> that tells of the Vah`shir Vampyre. It tells you that...<br>
