As far as Mistmoor's vampires...if you go by the EQRPG, some Houses of Neriak that want to court the Queen's favor send their children to Mistmoore to train to be Dark Necromancers or other servants. The Queen was a ally of Mistmoore so it explains where he gets his Tier`dal servants. If ou use invis to undead in Mistmoore you'll notice it doesn't work on all his servants....not all those T`ier dal you see are dead....they just have switched alliegences.<br>
