I guess that could even be used as a ingame reason why you can't walk more than two steps in Neriak without tripping over a Tier`dal that says they are a vampire these days. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
